Desiring a similar set of objects would open up the two nations to a larger surface area

17:48.600 --> 17:52.440
of competition and therefore potential conflict and even violence.

17:52.440 --> 17:58.880
And so, at the peak of Sino-American optimism in 2007, and this was right before 2008, where

17:58.880 --> 18:03.520
the congeniality between the East and the West had never been greater, Gerard stood

18:03.520 --> 18:09.800
against the crowd and warned us of such a conflict, a conflict that will come from the

18:09.800 --> 18:14.920
very mechanism that most thought would establish peace, trade.

